{"meta":{"title":"2 Néphi 14","canonicalUrl":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/14?lang=fra","contentType":"text/html","pageAttributes":{"data-asset-id":"99f8336aa50933b0dd72e89ebceea3ef2ab95e86","data-aid":"117823169","data-aid-version":"5","data-content-type":"chapter","data-uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/14","lang":"fra","data-orig-id":"aad669ae4a699b9a203f7fc9917f29ecfb153d79","xmlns:xsi":"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance"}},"content":{"head":{"page-meta-social":{"pageMeta":{"title":"2 Néphi 14","description":"Sion et ses filles seront rachetées et purifiées au millénium — Comparez avec Ésaïe 4. Vers 559–545 av. J.-C."},"pageSocial":{"title":"2 Néphi 14","description":"Sion et ses filles seront rachetées et purifiées au millénium — Comparez avec Ésaïe 4. Vers 559–545 av. J.-C."}},"links":[{"type":"array","rel":"stylesheet","orig-type":"text/css","href":"css/style_classic-scripture.css"}],"scripts":[]},"body":"<header>\n<p class=\"title-number\" data-aid=\"117823170\" id=\"title_number1\">Chapitre 14</p>\n<p class=\"study-summary\" data-aid=\"117823171\" id=\"study_summary1\">Sion et ses filles seront rachetées et purifiées au millénium — Comparez avec <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/isa/4?lang=fra\">Ésaïe 4</a>. Vers 559–545 av. J.-C.</p>\n</header>\n<div class=\"body-block\">\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"117823172\" id=\"p1\"><span class=\"verse-number\">1 </span>Et sept femmes saisiront en ce jour un seul homme, et diront : Nous mangerons notre pain, et nous nous vêtirons de nos habits ; fais-nous seulement porter ton nom ! Enlève notre <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note1a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>opprobre</a>.</p>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"117823173\" id=\"p2\"><span class=\"verse-number\">2 </span>En ce temps-là, le <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note2a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>germe</a> du Seigneur aura de la magnificence et de la gloire, et le fruit du pays de l’éclat et de la beauté pour les réchappés d’Israël.</p>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"117823174\" id=\"p3\"><span class=\"verse-number\">3 </span>Et ceux qui restent en Sion et demeurent en Jérusalem seront appelés saints, quiconque à Jérusalem sera inscrit parmi les vivants,</p>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"117823175\" id=\"p4\"><span class=\"verse-number\">4 </span><a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note4a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>après</a> que le Seigneur aura <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note4b\"><sup class=\"marker\">b</sup>lavé</a> les ordures des filles de Sion, et purifié Jérusalem du sang qui est au milieu d’elle, par le souffle de la justice et par le souffle de la <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note4c\"><sup class=\"marker\">c</sup>destruction</a>.</p>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"117823176\" id=\"p5\"><span class=\"verse-number\">5 </span>Le Seigneur établira, sur toute l’étendue de la montagne de Sion et sur les lieux d’assemblées, une <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note5a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>nuée</a> fumante pendant le jour, et un feu de flammes éclatantes pendant la nuit ; car tout ce qui est glorieux en Sion sera mis à couvert.</p>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"117823177\" id=\"p6\"><span class=\"verse-number\">6 </span>Il y aura un abri pour donner de l’ombre contre la chaleur du jour, pour servir de <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note6a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>refuge</a> et d’asile contre l’orage et la pluie.</p>\n</div>\n<footer class=\"study-notes\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"chapter\">\n<li data-marker=\"14\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"verse\">\n<li data-marker=\"1\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note1a\" data-full-marker=\"1a\">\n<p data-aid=\"117823178\" id=\"note1a_p1\"><small>CÀD</small> celle d’être non mariées et sans enfants.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"2\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note2a\" data-full-marker=\"2a\">\n<p data-aid=\"117823179\" id=\"note2a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/isa/60.21?lang=fra#p21\">És 60:21</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/3.5?lang=fra#p5\">2 Né 3:5</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/jacob/2.25?lang=fra#p25\">Jcb 2:25</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"4\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note4a\" data-full-marker=\"4a\">\n<p data-aid=\"117823180\" id=\"note4a_p1\"><small>CÀD</small> Lorsque le Seigneur aura purifié la terre.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"b\" id=\"note4b\" data-full-marker=\"4b\">\n<p data-aid=\"117823181\" id=\"note4b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/wash-washed-washings?lang=fra\"><small>GÉ</small> Laver</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"c\" id=\"note4c\" data-full-marker=\"4c\">\n<p data-aid=\"117823182\" id=\"note4c_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/mal/3.2-3?lang=fra#p2\">Mal 3:2–3</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/mal/4.1?lang=fra#p1\">4:1</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"5\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note5a\" data-full-marker=\"5a\">\n<p data-aid=\"117823183\" id=\"note5a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/ex/13.21?lang=fra#p21\">Ex 13:21</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"6\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note6a\" data-full-marker=\"6a\">\n<p data-aid=\"117823184\" id=\"note6a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/isa/25.4?lang=fra#p4\">És 25:4</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/115.6?lang=fra#p6\">D&amp;A 115:6</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</footer>","footnotes":{"note1a":{"id":"note1a","marker":"1a","pid":"117823172","context":"opprobre","text":"<p data-aid=\"117823178\" id=\"note1a_p1\"><small>CÀD</small> celle d’être non mariées et sans enfants.</p>"},"note2a":{"id":"note2a","marker":"2a","pid":"117823173","context":"germe","text":"<p data-aid=\"117823179\" id=\"note2a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/isa/60.21?lang=fra#p21\">És 60:21</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/3.5?lang=fra#p5\">2 Né 3:5</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/jacob/2.25?lang=fra#p25\">Jcb 2:25</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/ot/isa/60.21?lang=fra#p21","text":"És 60:21"},{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/3.5?lang=fra#p5","text":"2 Né 3:5"},{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/bofm/jacob/2.25?lang=fra#p25","text":"Jcb 2:25"}]},"note4a":{"id":"note4a","marker":"4a","pid":"117823175","context":"après","text":"<p data-aid=\"117823180\" id=\"note4a_p1\"><small>CÀD</small> Lorsque le Seigneur aura purifié la terre.</p>"},"note4b":{"id":"note4b","marker":"4b","pid":"117823175","context":"lavé","text":"<p data-aid=\"117823181\" id=\"note4b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/wash-washed-washings?lang=fra\"><small>GÉ</small> Laver</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/gs/wash-washed-washings?lang=fra","text":"GÉ Laver"}]},"note4c":{"id":"note4c","marker":"4c","pid":"117823175","context":"destruction","text":"<p data-aid=\"117823182\" id=\"note4c_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/mal/3.2-3?lang=fra#p2\">Mal 3:2–3</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/mal/4.1?lang=fra#p1\">4:1</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/ot/mal/3.2-3?lang=fra#p2","text":"Mal 3:2–3"},{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/ot/mal/4.1?lang=fra#p1","text":"4:1"}]},"note5a":{"id":"note5a","marker":"5a","pid":"117823176","context":"nuée","text":"<p data-aid=\"117823183\" id=\"note5a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/ex/13.21?lang=fra#p21\">Ex 13:21</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/ot/ex/13.21?lang=fra#p21","text":"Ex 13:21"}]},"note6a":{"id":"note6a","marker":"6a","pid":"117823177","context":"refuge","text":"<p data-aid=\"117823184\" id=\"note6a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/isa/25.4?lang=fra#p4\">És 25:4</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/115.6?lang=fra#p6\">D&amp;A 115:6</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/ot/isa/25.4?lang=fra#p4","text":"És 25:4"},{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/115.6?lang=fra#p6","text":"D&amp;A 115:6"}]}}},"pids":[["117823169",{"key":"117823169"}],["117823170",{"key":"117823170"}],["117823171",{"key":"117823171"}],["117823172",{"key":"117823172"}],["117823173",{"key":"117823173"}],["117823174",{"key":"117823174"}],["117823175",{"key":"117823175"}],["117823176",{"key":"117823176"}],["117823177",{"key":"117823177"}],["117823178",{"key":"117823178"}],["117823179",{"key":"117823179"}],["117823180",{"key":"117823180"}],["117823181",{"key":"117823181"}],["117823182",{"key":"117823182"}],["117823183",{"key":"117823183"}],["117823184",{"key":"117823184"}]],"tableOfContentsUri":"/scriptures/bofm","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/14"}